T02D3264:19a-1: mee tri ya s'a dha nam /
T02D3264:19a-4: sngar bshad pa'i tshogs zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
T02D3264:19a-5: du yi ge mem ser po yongs su gyur pa
T02D3264:19a-6: las sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis sna tshogs padma
T02D3264:19a-7: la bzhugs pa / zhal gsum ma /
T02D3264:19a-8: spyan gsum phyag bzhi pa g-yas pa dang g-yon pa'i zhal ni nag pa dang dkar ba /
T02D3264:19a-10: phyag gnyis kyis chos bshad ba'i phyag rgya mdzad pa /
T02D3264:19a-11: g-yas pa dang g-yon pa'i phyag gzhan gnyis kyis ni mchog sbyin pa dang /
T02D3264:19a-12: me tog rgyas pa'i klu shing gi yal ga mdzes pa bsnams pa /
T02D3264:19a-13: sna tshogs pa'i rgyan dang ldan pa'i byams pa'i skur
T02D3264:19a-14: bdag nyid dmigs la phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste
T02D3264:19a-15: / lag pa gnyis kyi sor mo khu tshur bsdams
T02D3264:19a-16: la mdzub mo gnyis mthe bong dag gi dbus su
T02D3264:19a-17: mchog tu gnas pas me tog gi rnam pa ltar
T02D3264:19a-18: / gshibs pa'o // de nas bzlas pa bya ste /
T02D3264:19a-19: aom mem mee tri ya sv'a h'a /
